# Week 02 - AWS Core Services

## Learning Objectives

Learn how to deploy and manage fundamental AWS resources.

## Activities

## IAM

Practiced:

- Creating IAM Users.
- Managing Roles.
- Configuring Policies.
- Understanding Least Privilege principle.


## Amazon EC2

Hands-on:

- Launch EC2 instances.
- Configure Security Groups.
- Connect to virtual servers.


## Amazon S3

Practiced:

- Creating S3 Buckets.
- Uploading objects.
- Managing storage permissions.


## Key Outcomes

- Basic AWS resource management.
- Understanding AWS security model.
